Package: glycoverse
Title: Easy Install and Load the `Glycoverse`
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Bin", "Fu", , "23110220018@m.fudan.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"),
            comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8567-2997"))
Description: The 'glycoverse' is a set of packages that together form a
    comprehensive pipeline for glycomics and glycoproteomics data analysis.
    This package is designed to make it easy to install and load multiple
    'glycoverse' packages in a single step.
